description:
Where fit, comfort, and firmness come together to give you jaw-dropping results, this Maidenform Body Shaper is a must-have for any wardrobe. Unlike most shapewear that squeezes everything in and makes you feel like your body is trapped, our this body shaper has a power mesh lining that is so comfortable--you will forget you have it on. The lacy, lingerie-style fabric around the breast and upper torso is sexy and looks great under a sheer or revealing top. Slip on Maidenform's Body Shaper to turn up the wow factor while at work or at play. Style #1456

  • Provides firm control and shaping with a built-in bra
  • Back adjustable semi-rigid straps
  • Two-ply front-lined with power mesh
  • Luxurious fabric feels fabulous against your skin
  • Power mesh liner for all-over control
  • Three-section unlined built-in bra cups
  • Lined at gusset
  • Hook-and-eye gusset prevents garment slippage for stay-in-place confidence
  • Elegant, lingerie-style shapewear
  • (Formerly Flexees by Maidenform)
  • Nylon/elastane, cops:polyester; lining:cotton
  • Hand wash
  • Imported
